name: Traveler

The boy Twin (You can change this if you are willing) 

A Traveler on a desperate mission to find his lost missing sister, even though they had met the last two times, Lumine refuses to go with him until he explores this entire world. Or Lunime feels like they belong in this world..

Aether is a tall-medium figure, he has a far-skin of tan, slim body build structure. His striking eyes were golden-yellow eyes.
